title: 2 Bedroom / 2 Bath condo
posting_body: ['Welcome to your beachfront condo!', 'Come and enjoy everything South Florida has to offer.', 'This 2 Bedroom / 2 Bath condo is well maintained and professionally managed.', 'Just a few minutes away from local restaurants, bars and other amenities.', 'Sip your morning coffee on your ocean front balcony and watch the waves roll in.', 'Owner is looking for new tenant(s) that are ready to enjoy the beachfront lifestyle.', 'Non-smokers please and no pets allowed per owners request.', 'Washer / Dryer in unit.', '1500 S Ocean Blvd # 1007 POMPANO BEACH, FL 33062-7418', 'PROPERTY ID:  GTF10339161', 'Type of Property: CONDO', 'List Price:\t$2,800', 'Bedrooms:  2', 'Bathrooms: 2', 'SqFt (Liv):1,250', 'CALL OR TEXT TODAY', 'show contact info', 'Global Trust Realty, LLC posts properties for a 30 day period of time.', ' Due to current high rental demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, cancelled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', ' All prices are subject to change based upon availability.', 'All information is deemed to be correct but not guaranteed.', 'Listed and Brokered by:The Keyes Company']
